title: Grateful Dead Live at Kingswood Music Theater on 1984-06-21
lineage: Master Cassettes (Nakamichi 700 MKii) > Oade modified Grace Design Lunatec V3 > M-Audio MicroTrack II > WAV 24/96
description:
Set I
Hell In A Bucket
They Love Each Other
C.C. Rider >
Bird Song
Beat It On Down The Line
Dupree's Diamond Blues
Looks Like Rain >
Might As Well
Set II
Scarlet Begonias >
Fire On The Mountain
Never Trust A Woman
Samson & Delilah >
Terrapin Station >
Drums >
Space >
The Wheel >
Throwing Stones >
Not Fade Away
New Orleans *
Big Boss Man > $
Iko Iko $
Wavy Gravy Dedication

 
Comment
The Band opened
SEVA Foundation benefit
Last time performed & first performance since November 11, 1970 *

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
Rick Danko - Guitar $
Levon Helm - Harmonica $
